<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>فَسَنُيَسِّرُهُ لِلْعُسْرى <span class="c2">(١٠)</span><a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
